---
title: Greek Gyro Skewers with Roasted Zucchini, Baked Pita Chips, and Cucumber Tzatziki
description: You know those big spinning rotisseries of slow-cooking meat? Well, this is a mini version! We’ve incorporated a bit of Greek yogurt for a tangy flavor and whipped up a homemade tzatziki so good you’ll be tempted to double (or triple) dip the skewers, zucchini, and chips. OPA!
